The apricot cream pie is an unobtainable item that is wielded during a cutscene in The Fremennik Isles. During the quest, the player is required to act as the jester for Mawnis Burowgar, in order to eavesdrop on the guards' conversation. When choosing the "Pie" option, the apricot cream pie appears during the animation.

Gallery[edit | edit source]

  • Pie animation during The Fremennik Isles

Trivia[edit | edit source]

  • It is a reference to Pieing, a prank of throwing a cream or custard pie in somebody's face that is often done by circus clowns.
